/nffgs/{nffgName}/links/{linkName}




/nodes

/nodes/{nodeName}

/nodes/{nodeName}/reachableHosts

/nodes/{nodeName}/links






Resources
=========

hosts                                       all hosts in the NFV System
hosts -> {hostName}                         a single host
hosts -> {hostName} -> nodes                all nodes allocated on host

connections                                 all connections in the NFV System
connections -> {connectionName}             a single connection in the NFV System

vnfs                                        all VNFs in the NFV System
vnfs -> {vnfName}                           a single VNF

nffgs                                       all nffg in the system
nffgs -> {nffgName}                         a single nffg
nffgs -> {nffgName} -> nodes                all nodes in this nffg
nffgs -> {nffgName} -> links                all links in this nffg

nodes                                       all nodes in the NFV System
nodes -> {nodeName}                         a single node
nodes -> {nodeName} -> links                all links with this node as the source node
nodes -> {nodeName} -> links -> {linkName}  a single link
